    <section class="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="faq-header">
                <p class="headerline-1">YOU HAVE</p>
                <p class="headerline-2">QUESTIONS</p>
                <p class="headerline-3">WE HAVE ANSWERS</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-accordion">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>How does the website know where to plant the tree?</span>

                        <svg width="15" height="10" viewBox="0 0 42 25">
                            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="black" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We use real-time climate data (temperature, rainfall, and soil type). If you pick a location,
                            we cross-reference it with our botanical database to recommend trees that are scientifically
                            proven to thrive there.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>Can I track the exact tree I planted?</span>

                        <svg width="15" height="10" viewBox="0 0 42 25">
                            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="black" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>While we cannot tag every single sapling with GPS for cost reasons, we provide the precise
                            coordinates of the reforestation block where your contribution was planted, along with
                            photos of the project site.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>Can I gift a tree to someone else?</span>

                        <svg width="15" height="10" viewBox="0 0 42 25">
                            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="black" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! During the payment process, you can choose to send the digital certificate and
                            the "Location Match" report to a friend or family member as a sustainable gift.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question">
                        <span>What happens after I donate?</span>

                        <svg width="15" height="10" viewBox="0 0 42 25">
                            <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="black" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Your funds are held securely until the next planting season for that specific region. We then
                            disburse the funds to our certified local partners who purchase the saplings and manage the
                            planting process.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

